The '''Healer's Guild''' was a organization from the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] that composed of healers from [[Planet/Legends|planets]] and [[Species/Legends|species]] across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. The Guild used the [[Spice/Legends|spice]] [[Carsunum/Legends|carsunum]] to control and prevent the proliferation of [[hive virus]]es, including the hive virus that infected the crew of the [[Katana fleet]]. The Guild disappeared with the emergence of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].<ref name="FTS">{{JournalCite|2|The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos}}</ref>

